  <h2>"Admitting tomorrow's leaders, today."</h2>
  <p>St Francis Girls Suwerwa is one of the leading schools in Kenya — known for academic excellence, social development, and all-around growth. We admit students from across the country and abroad, operating as a national school under the Kenyan Education system.</p>
