<p>It is worth noting that admission to St Francis Girls Suwerwa is <strong>not solely based on academic performance</strong>. The school encourages and supports students' all-around development, and therefore considers other factors such as co-curricular activities, community service, and leadership skills.</p>

<p>SFGS is dedicated to offering quality education and a conducive learning environment to its students. The school's admission process is carefully designed to ensure that only the most deserving students join the SFGS family — and this commitment to selection has contributed to the school's excellent academic performance and outstanding reputation over the years.</p>

<h2 class="section-heading">What Guides Our Admission</h2>
<div class="principles-grid">
