  <div class="principle-card"><span class="principle-icon">✝️</span><h3>Christian Values</h3><p>Alignment with our Christian ethos and willingness to participate in spiritual life.</p></div>
  <div class="principle-card"><span class="principle-icon">🌟</span><h3>Holistic Potential</h3><p>Demonstrated growth in sports, arts, leadership, and community engagement.</p></div>
</div>

